{"tid":412311,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好享受同鍾意獨處既時間？","createTime":"2017-09-24T14:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T11:43:08.000Z","uid":102938,"like":146,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"321327cd4f0b03e88644ad8cde59ff6a5f6538bf","tid":412311,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:06:10.000Z","msg":"由細到大，雖然都鍾意一班人玩，但亦好享受獨處既時間<br />\n小學會一個人去圖書館、電腦室、參加活動、落街打波踢波公園玩<br />\n到中學，有時放假會一個人去行街，主要係game、卡、漫畫鋪等<br />\n最重點真係會自己一個人去網吧打機，信長守城CS巨商AOC彩虹等<br />\n放學有時去，考試早放更加必去，好享受一個人打機既時間<br />\n然後又會一個人去餐廳M記大快活食野，坐好耐又得<br />\n到完左中學，到大專、大學時代，超級享受一個人去圖書館坐<br />\n有時會hea陣做功課，睇書、睇新聞，片、FB，打陣機之類<br />\n最勁試過一個人去食放題明將邊爐行山，果段時間真係好寧靜好輕鬆<br />\n到全職工作後，有陣時星期六返半日放工，又會一個人去食野<br />\n甚至如果知道聽日放假，會專登坐係港鐵站坐番一個鐘先走<br />\n總之就係好鍾意獨處既時間，唔知有無巴絲都一樣？"},{"pid":"47d1c929b0e0f9b7b280f82682d1e70ab8491045","tid":412311,"uid":41737,"like":2,"dislike":57,"score":-55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c3ca82a48dedd97cce8a7a66236e576206f71ae","tid":412311,"uid":102938,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  A0死毒撚 日撚日係到ff識到女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔洗咁激動，小弟雖然自問係毒，但都拍過幾次拖<br />\n而且都一樣鍾意一大班人放題邊爐唱K燒野食韓燒咩都好，都好玩<br />\n只係有陣時返學或返工真係太chur太累，真係想獨處寧靜一下"},{"pid":"e62a809891099d81ee29f8d77db9766d6e5f705b","tid":412311,"uid":62948,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"講中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  讀書個時會自己去香港一日游，最記得係坐叮叮由總站坐至尾站，再鳩行，見到啱返屋企路線既車就上，聽住歌，成個世界好似得自己咁。<br />\n<br />\n而家人大左就最happy 係早放工，一個人去搵食，食咩都得，成程唔使諗野，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排讀返書，都會同成班同學圍威喂，但因為半工讀，私人時間少左成半，所以更珍惜自己一個既時間，最鍾意係返學之前食餐好既，再去圖書館溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2ebb3fe3a8cdedeba9ff18b7305cddcaff69b3","tid":412311,"uid":127116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"獨處真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1260a9f61942c3ee6b1b7b7b067e084c953db48","tid":412311,"uid":2833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n獨處真係好正<br />\n<br />\n利申：依家自己一個係曼谷玩緊"},{"pid":"d44857ea48e7fbaf4734ce430e05a8e7408c240b","tid":412311,"uid":56320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"自己睇戲 睇乜都得<br />\n去掃街 食乜都得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd72f68e06286525dd6c8fb37ba0260af7e2395","tid":412311,"uid":56320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"去旅行又係<br />\n唔洗就人<br />\n試過去廿幾日先返<br />\n真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86f490919f003fe166873c11ddd9d0904e7b76d","tid":412311,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行又係<br />\n唔洗就人<br />\n試過去廿幾日先返<br />\n真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇撚有錯<br />\n想點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1192b7bcc32ce6752867c97155bccb84ee68a749","tid":412311,"uid":11760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去旅行又係<br />\n唔洗就人<br />\n試過去廿幾日先返<br />\n真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇撚有錯<br />\n想點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺<br />\n去邊又唔洗就人<br />\n玩到攰就死返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323af99ee7dd3edeffc512101b2b78d00fe30b78","tid":412311,"uid":62948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去旅行又係<br />\n唔洗就人<br />\n試過去廿幾日先返<br />\n真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇撚有錯<br />\n想點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺<br />\n去邊又唔洗就人<br />\n玩到攰就死返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旅行原意係想休息，但對住d friend 都會攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34b55f10186be710da5bd198a4e10566cd8667a","tid":412311,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"我都好鐘意獨處 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75af3e7d11c5b2e6adb70918a43342ed45d50cce","tid":412311,"uid":146420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  讀書個時會自己去香港一日游，最記得係坐叮叮由總站坐至尾站，再鳩行，見到啱返屋企路線既車就上，聽住歌，成個世界好似得自己咁。<br />\n<br />\n而家人大左就最happy 係早放工，一個人去搵食，食咩都得，成程唔使諗野，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排讀返書，都會同成班同學圍威喂，但因為半工讀，私人時間少左成半，所以更珍惜自己一個既時間，最鍾意係返學之前食餐好既，再去圖書館溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n獨處真心好正 可以自己一個人沉澱下心情 無拘無束 一個人靜下幾好👍🏿"},{"pid":"296fc28cd469cfa4b9bf0c402b81170e354e783d","tid":412311,"uid":126724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗就人唔洗睇人面色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有正常社交同好朋友<br />\n但由小學已經鐘意一個人睇戲食飯<br />\n依家獨居緊仲正好享受同自己相處嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982363203d38b4b8449d6ced6c1291ea3ff737ea","tid":412311,"uid":24428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"以前份工永遠都係自己一個 <br />\n會覺得好撚悶 好想有人同自己傾下計<br />\n依家轉咗第份工 反而好珍惜獨處嘅時間<br />\n一個人睇戲好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccad2c953e38505c89353e22c9a8f8f0918b3e9","tid":412311,"uid":71496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n細個好鐘意自閉<br />\n但愈大發現自己一個開始無咩做<br />\n再無咩有熱誠既野做<br />\n年齡愈大<br />\n身邊愈黎愈多人有拖拍<br />\n就愈怕自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071a4acd7e26deed50d34a716e864db5b46415f4","tid":412311,"uid":102938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"就好似依家夜晚獨自上連登，感覺已經良好，又樂趣多"},{"pid":"3cd4ad9bee7382f9d0041b7ceacc3aa591f5d007","tid":412311,"uid":96511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好舒服"},{"pid":"5065fc1c51a7954bfa7187403713e34e24b2a1a0","tid":412311,"uid":25036,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:30:17.000Z","msg":"好鐘意自己一個周街走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如我冇親戚朋友係新界西<br />\n但係我會特登自己一個入去屯元天去探索未知既領域<br />\n<br />\n自己去一啲未去過既地方就會好有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcad64833e0f33d69441265a08cb71e3a4daed9a","tid":412311,"uid":106450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66603393cfe57fb665bb4b591c54eaa354f5c222","tid":412311,"uid":86008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識人對我黎講係一件好攰嘅事<br />\n唔想social 作無謂嘅交際 唔想理其他人嘅事<br />\n習慣左自己一個人<br />\n唔洗就住就住 唔洗理人點睇我 想做乜就乜<br />\n直程想成世獨處算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有時會情緒泛濫覺得有d寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b348471242dff30f5100c39ac671405a416fe118","tid":412311,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"無呀，孤獨得太耐，想識朋友，女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c273499a2ee2ed0261e8ac3ca21af93d503aabc1","tid":412311,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"會遊車河 自己突登<br />\n坐下電車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  坐去筲箕灣 再撘返返去"},{"pid":"5c6ebac563ff4d2ea451b0a0a4fabc289c125145","tid":412311,"uid":136332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"想享受係可以好享受嘅<br />\n時不時會自己一個睇戲、食飯、睇展、聽concert<br />\n但係獨處得太耐又會需要有人同我傾吓計<br />\n可能自己啲思想太黑暗點都要有人拉返自己出嚟"},{"pid":"a784fbe8adb37010d1ffcca02ecc3cc02af8f1fa","tid":412311,"uid":146995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"雖然習慣獨處，<br />\n但係都同時等緊能夠一直陪自己周圍去 傾心事嘅對像"},{"pid":"c91c80fb417c1c7f1d0c86c5e918b179eba36deb","tid":412311,"uid":39511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"我有時都會係地鐵月台坐半鐘先出閘<br />\n<br />\n明明係準備返屋企 但就係有個感覺覺得好攰想抖下<br />\n<br />\n坐完之後個人會開心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8c8722741a59e855324e6bde8a628cb9fc14c6","tid":412311,"uid":58830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有時都會係地鐵月台坐半鐘先出閘<br />\n<br />\n明明係準備返屋企 但就係有個感覺覺得好攰想抖下<br />\n<br />\n坐完之後個人會開心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel"},{"pid":"5349f2ac86b7a5894d6c07b00d4696bace2e59b2","tid":412311,"uid":125024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然習慣獨處，<br />\n但係都同時等緊能夠一直陪自己周圍去 傾心事嘅對像</blockquote><br />\n岩啊 自己一個係開心<br />\n但話真係唔想人陪就假既<br />\n係懶得去r人 見啲fd 拍曬拖又唔想痴住佢地<br />\n其實個心等緊一個岩傾 唔係時時刻刻要一齊 但得閒可以出下黎玩既人"},{"pid":"ebbd87fb28d5fbbb4799cde2bf28c13119042bc5","tid":412311,"uid":42119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  A0死毒撚 日撚日係到ff識到女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？</blockquote><br />\n會講鍾意獨處先唔係毒撚<br />\n因為代表佢地有正常社交<br />\n有時我地呢d冇得揀既毒撚睇見獨處post真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"30cc02d82762e33daed1a5ada43d19f37b060c64","tid":412311,"uid":102938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"今日辛苦完一日返工，又係時候需要獨處一陣比自己調整一下心情了<br />\n大家捱多幾日就有國慶假啦"},{"pid":"4b4692856de181e5ce049e549f8854d0d248936d","tid":412311,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  A0死毒撚 日撚日係到ff識到女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？</blockquote><br />\n會講鍾意獨處先唔係毒撚<br />\n因為代表佢地有正常社交<br />\n有時我地呢d冇得揀既毒撚睇見獨處post真係得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n冇錯"},{"pid":"61acd1579622b90d422fffec200f2b552a809ba6","ti